  <mainDescription>&lt;h3>&#xD;
    Using motivators with test plan and test case records&#xD;
&lt;/h3>&#xD;
&lt;div>&#xD;
    &lt;p>&#xD;
        A motivator provides the rationale for some or all of the testing. In Rational ClearQuest Test Manager, this&#xD;
        information can be provided as a test motivator file or a &lt;span class=&quot;keyword&quot;>Rational ClearQuest&lt;/span>&#xD;
        requirement.&#xD;
    &lt;/p>&#xD;
    &lt;p>&#xD;
        A test motivator file is an external file that provides details about a test plan or test case. For example, a test&#xD;
        motivator file could be a Word document or Excel spreadsheet containing detailed information about a specific test&#xD;
        plan or test case. You can reference a test motivator file from a test plan and test case record using a &lt;span         class=&quot;keyword&quot;>Rational ClearQuest Client&lt;/span> or a &lt;span class=&quot;keyword&quot;>Rational ClearQuest Client for&#xD;
        Eclipse&lt;/span>. Before you can associate a test motivator file with a test plan or test case record, you must&#xD;
        create a file location record to define the path to the test motivator file.&#xD;
    &lt;/p>&#xD;
    &lt;p>&#xD;
        If you are using the Rational RequisitePro integration version 1.8 with Rational ClearQuest or the Rational&#xD;
        ClearQuest Enterprise schema version 7.0, you can use any Rational ClearQuest client to associate a &lt;span         class=&quot;keyword&quot;>Rational ClearQuest&lt;/span> requirement record with a test plan, test case, or configured test case&#xD;
        record.&#xD;
    &lt;/p>&#xD;
    &lt;div class=&quot;p&quot;>&#xD;
        You can use associations between test plan and test case record with a test motivator to determine: &#xD;
        &lt;ul>&#xD;
            &lt;li>&#xD;
                If there is test coverage for the motivator&#xD;
            &lt;/li>&#xD;
            &lt;li>&#xD;
                If a test plan associated with a motivator has an associated external file (Excel or Word document)&#xD;
            &lt;/li>&#xD;
        &lt;/ul>&#xD;
    &lt;/div>&#xD;
    &lt;p>&#xD;
        For more information about test motivator files, see the Help system for the &lt;span class=&quot;keyword&quot;>Rational&#xD;
        ClearQuest Client&lt;/span> or the &lt;span class=&quot;keyword&quot;>Rational ClearQuest Client for Eclipse&lt;/span>.&#xD;
    &lt;/p>&#xD;
&lt;/div></mainDescription>
</org.eclipse.epf.uma:ContentDescription>
